RelatedSentence: Kaiser Permanente Hawaii today announced the addition of three new physicians who join over 500 care providers within the state 's largest medical group , the Hawaii Permanente Medical Group ( HPMG ) , which provides comprehensive care to Kaiser Permanente 's 235,000 - plus members in Hawaii .
